' Estrutura de módulos: examples/architecture-overview.puml + architecture*.puml (v0.11.10+); ver docs/architecture-diagrams.md.
title Sample for visual pipeline (sequence)

actor User
participant "API Gateway" as Api
database Postgres

User -> Api: GET /items
Api -> Postgres: SELECT
Postgres --> Api: rows
Api --> User: 200 JSON

